<ab>48. In the Workshop with other apprentices, <lb/>
honor a Contract never to quarrel; <lb/>
even if you are the best, help the worse ones<lb/>
maintain the tools in the Workshop.<lb/>
Pay attention to the Master’s Palette and Brushes, <lb/>
to cleaning and preparing canvases and panels, <lb/>
to grinding pigments finely, to keeping them clean,<lb/>
and not to temper ashes and smalts too much.<lb/>
